# Capacitor regenerates these on `cap sync` and stores them with LF. Pin LF so
# Windows checkouts (autocrlf) don't surface a phantom CRLF-only diff every time
# git touches them. Targeted on purpose — no repo-wide renormalization.
*.gradle text eol=lf

# Generated by tools/scripts/gen-spec-status.mjs with LF-only newlines (spec
# 0058). The doc-integrity freshness guard does a raw byte-for-byte compare of
# the committed ledger against the generator's LF render, so pin LF here or a
# Windows autocrlf checkout (CRLF) would fail the guard locally while passing on
# Linux CI. Targeted on purpose.
/docs/specs/STATUS.md text eol=lf
